{"tid":1474447,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"建議重推租者置其屋計劃","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:01:53.000Z","uid":48776,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dedc3315b98bc496071ee5d21d4ca917f394cfea","tid":1474447,"uid":48776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"林鄭聽取<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建制派施政報告建議</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n陳振英建議，政府應重推租者置其屋計劃，讓公屋租戶可買入現時居住的單位，並把多出的房間租出，減少劏房問題。至於維修方面問題，他建議無論是否屬於買入的單位，都一概由政府負責維修費用。他形容，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭對此建議很感興趣。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">準備訓街啦香港人</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8b260d460d01e7edab6435621bae5bce38e52f88","tid":1474447,"uid":48776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2426901?fbclid=IwAR0m2K9LS8h1iQGQORzm7FOJC0cJpzHGbS0uO0J_kbluQqWTEOeGArQyR-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2426901%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0m2K9LS8h1iQGQORzm7FOJC0cJpzHGbS0uO0J_kbluQqWTEOeGArQyR-c&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdpo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=360f6a2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2426901?fbclid=IwAR0m2K9LS8h1iQGQORzm7FOJC0cJpzHGbS0uO0J_kbluQqWTEOeGArQyR-c</a>"},{"pid":"68bd6f6a52dfefee2e898c1d61da9e6c317ac956","tid":1474447,"uid":48776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b26649f55eb110d0de6e53493b8e0ee8588da78","tid":1474447,"uid":224510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，香港人公屋都排唔到<br />\n新移民仲可以買起作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae1c851057ef85223ee87935bf878dc7320c1c5","tid":1